  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Main] Trigger \uFF1CDe-Digivolve 3\uFF1E on 1 of your
    opponent's Digimon. (Trash up to 3 cards from the top of one of your opponent's
    Digimon. If it has no digivolution cards, or becomes a level 3 Digimon, you can't
    trash any more cards.) Then, delete all of your opponent's Digimon with play
    costs of 3 or less."
